b'MD Student Services and Support'
b'tlowery1'
b'Student Affairs'
b'The mission of Student Affairs in the College of Medicine is to help students identify and accomplish their academic, career and personal goals. We achieve this mission by providing exemplary student services, resources, counseling, guidance and advocacy, and by addressing our students\xe2\x80\x99 diverse backgrounds, experiences, and needs. In collaboration and in partnership with medical education leaders, faculty members, students, and other stakeholders in medical education, we strive to create an appropriately supportive, welcoming, nurturing, enriching, challenging and inclusive environment in which students have a voice to express their perspectives and concerns.'
